<div style="width:700px;margin:50px auto;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding: 40px;border-radius:3px;background:white;word-break: break-all;">

<%= link_to "Sign in", '/users/sign_in' %><br />
<%= link_to "Sign up", '/users/sign_up' %><br />

<hr>

<h3>Get token</h3>

<b>POST</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/sessions
</pre>
Params => {"user": {"email": "admin@example.com", "password": "12345678"}}

<p>If the email and password is correct the server will respond with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Logged in","user":{"id":1,"email":"admin@example.com","token":"76e740aecc5ed1e6163e10e91f84f03a","created_at":"2015-03-03T16:09:32.712Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T18:12:14.166Z"}}
</pre>

<h3>Delete token</h3>

<b>DELETE</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/sessions/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Logged out"}
</pre>

<hr>

<h3>All Articles</h3>

<b>GET</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/articles/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with an array with all articles belonging to the user</p>

<pre>
{"info":"authenticated","article":[{"id":4,"title":"test","content":"test","created_at":"2015-03-03T16:30:22.818Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T16:30:22.818Z","user_id":1},{"id":6,"title":"test123","content":"test","created_at":"2015-03-03T17:31:16.071Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T17:58:43.953Z","user_id":1},{"id":7,"title":"test","content":"test","created_at":"2015-03-03T17:57:37.855Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T17:57:37.855Z","user_id":1}]}
</pre>

<h3>A specific article</h3>

<b>GET</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/articles/show/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>
Params => {"article": {"id": "1"}}

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Article showed","article":{"id":6,"title":"test123","content":"test","created_at":"2015-03-03T17:31:16.071Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T17:58:43.953Z","user_id":1}}
</pre>

<h3>Create an article</h3>

<b>POST</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/articles/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>
Params => {"article": {"title": "sometitle", "content": "somecontent"}}

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Article created"}
</pre>

<h3>Update an article</h3>

<b>PUT</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/articles/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>
Params => {"article": {"id": "1", title": "sometitle", "content": "somecontent"}}

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Article updated","article":{"id":6,"title":"test","content":"some","created_at":"2015-03-03T17:31:16.071Z","updated_at":"2015-03-03T19:35:01.574Z","user_id":1}}
</pre>

<h3>Destroy an article</h3>

<b>DELETE</b>
<pre>
	www.example.com/articles/{user_id}?token={token}
</pre>
Params => {"article": {"id": "1"}}

<p>If the token and id is correct the server will respond with with the following attributes</p>

<pre>
{"info":"Article destroyed"}
</pre>





</div>